This module is part of p3ctrl.v. It converts the mux selections for SN, CPU, 
and FWD to the corresponing "inverse" selections for ping, pang, and pong.

Basically, this is here to implement the rule that:
"If agent A selects buffer P, then buffer P selects agent A"
